Name: Loco Launcher
About the game: Pick and choose an animal to play as, then shoot it out of a cannon, have it ride in a vehicle or giant rock, or simply bust through walls to destroy buildings as fast as possible! As you destroy things, you'll be faced with rubble and other obstacles to fight against as the time runs out. The animal you choose will have abilities to help destroy everything in its path.
